silu, aby ma opäť oživila.

33
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:58,260
Hľadala som ťa sto rokov.

34
00:04:09,420 --> 00:04:11,019
Naozaj si Yuan Tao?

35
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,760
Si naozaj nažive?

36
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,920
Myslela som, že si zomrel.

37
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,880
Nemyslela som si, že by
som ťa mohla znovu vidieť.

38
00:04:33,900 --> 00:04:34,539
Yuan Tao,

39
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,100
ale..

40
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,000
