64
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,840
Prečo ti to moja matka
dáva stále za vinu?

65
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:04,020
To kvôli nej!

66
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,080
Pretože si ma zradil!

67
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:12,300
Prečo ťa Prekliatie slivkového
kvetu nezranilo...

68
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:15,680
Nepomyslel si na to, Yu Yan,

69
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:20,100
