118
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:41,659
Čo tým chceš povedať?

119
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:45,520
Yuan Tao,

120
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:48,640
Ja...

121
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:56,840
