122
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,160
Čo to hovoríš?

123
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,480
Najskôr som tomu neveril,

124
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:08,560
ale tu,

125
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,439
nebol som si istý,

126
00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:13,800
no Prekliatie slivkového kvetu
dalo odpoveď môjmu srdcu.

127
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:22,959
Zheng, rýchlo uteč!

128
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,280
Qiong Hua!

129
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:28,680
Qiong Hua!

130
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:32,319
Xiao Hei!

131
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,420
Rýchlo odveď Zheng!

132
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,680
Sestrička Zheng,

133
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,319
poďme.

134
00:09:35,620 --> 00:09:36,460
Neodídem.

135
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:37,959
Pomôžem Yu Yanovi!

136
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:47,780
Dosť!

137
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:48,920
Čo chceš robiť?

138
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:51,460
Uzamknem ťa pomocou
magického plátna.

139
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:53,760
Len ty?

140
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:55,439
Skúsim to!

141
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:59,580
Magické plátno! Uzamkni démona.

142
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:18,040
Uzamknem ťa do magického plátna
na sto rokov.

143
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,020
Nie... na tisíc rokov!

144
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,680
Zheng!

145
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,240
Okamžite ju pusti!

146
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:22,900
Pustiť ju?

147
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:25,040
Zabila toľko nevinných dievčat

148
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:26,840
