149
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:28,580
Myslíš, že ju nechám ísť?

150
00:10:39,380 --> 00:10:40,000
Neprenasleduj ju!

151
00:10:41,460 --> 00:10:42,360
Už je preč!

152
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:47,700
Aký je tvoj vzťah s ňou?

153
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:51,680
Nechcem o tom hovoriť!

154
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:53,540
Yu Yan, zastav sa!

155
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:55,680
Vtedy...

156
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:58,160
slová, ktoré mi povedal...

157
00:10:59,180 --> 00:11:00,959
bolo to kvôli nej, však?

158
00:11:03,780 --> 00:11:04,420
Povedal si,

159
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:06,800
že ma máš rád.

160
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,960
Je to pretože...

161
00:11:10,540 --> 00:11:12,599
vyzerám ako žena, ktorú si predtým miloval?

162
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,160
Tá žena...

163
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,080
je ona! Mám pravdu?

164
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:26,340
Odpovedz mi.

165
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,300
Hovor!

166
00:11:29,580 --> 00:11:30,720
Hovor!

167
00:11:32,940 --> 00:11:34,020
Nemám ti čo povedať.

168
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,260
Yu Yan,

169
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:37,000
si zbabelec!

170
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:40,580
Bez ohľadu na to, ako silne vyzeráš,

171
00:11:41,140 --> 00:11:44,240
si len zbabelec, ktorý sa neodvažuje
nahliadnuť do svojej minulosti.

172
00:11:52,340 --> 00:11:52,840
Áno.

173
00:11:53,700 --> 00:11:54,840
Som zbabelec!

174
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,520
Nemôžem byť ako ty a Bai Sheng...

175
00:11:57,720 --> 00:12:00,200
Nemôžem to len tak povedať!
Nemôžem!

176
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:03,900
Ak to dnes nebola Yuan Tao,

177
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:06,339
ak vtedy naozaj zomrela...

178
00:12:07,380 --> 00:12:09,240
tiež nemôžem byť s tebou.

179
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:12,160
Pretože ona bude navždy
žiť v mojej krvi!

180
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:14,520
V mojom živote...

181
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,340
a v mojich spomienkach!

182
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,020
Prečo si jej potom nedovolil,
aby ma zabila?

183
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:21,500
Mal si ju nechať, aby ma zabila!

184
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,680
Zabi ma!

185
00:12:22,860 --> 00:12:24,500
Prečo jej nedovolíš, aby ma zabila?

186
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:31,020
Nebudeš ma nútiť!

187
00:12:31,020 --> 00:12:32,020
Pýtam sa ťa...

188
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:36,340
Ak nebude zmluva s magickým plátnom,

189
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:39,940
